# Files excluded from the Posit Connect Cloud bundle.
# scripts/refresh_data.R is a BUILD-TIME tool: it library()s neonUtilities to
# rebuild data/sites/*.rds. The deployed app is bundle-only (loads the committed
# rds), so excluding it keeps the heavy neonUtilities dependency out of the
# manifest and the runtime image.
scripts/
refresh_data.log
.Rproj.user/
.Rhistory
